snippet.title: 30 Seconds From the First 30 Episodes of “The Amber Ruffin Show”
snippet.description:
The Amber Ruffin Show. Streaming on Peacock https://pck.tv/3pOiao8
Reserve your spot in the live studio audience for The Amber Ruffin Show at https://1iota.com/show/1210/the-amber

The Amber Ruffin Show never ceases to amaze us. Watch 30 seconds from the first 30 episodes to see what makes Amber Ruffin and her right hand man, Tarik Davis, so captivating. Take a look!

Show Synopsis: Amber showcases her signature smart-and-silly take on the news of the week, responding to it all with a charming, late-night mix of seriousness, nonsense, and evening gowns.

#PeacockTV #AmberRuffin #LateNight
